<L>__{exterior machine gun nest bridge night}
<A>__{sarge, upham and reiben sit with ryan in the darkness. ryan is lost in thought, far away. one after another, miller's men eye him.}
<C>__{sarge}
<D>__{private, i'm sorry about your brothers.}
<A>__{ryan nods. then, with some difficulty, he makes the trip from iowa back to france. he turns to sarge. ryan what was the name of the guy who got killed coming up here?}
<C>__{sarge}
<D>__{wade.}
<C>__{ryan}
<D>__{wade. huh, he died coming up here to keep me alive...i never met him...he didn't know me from adam, strange. what was he like?}
<C>__{sarge}
<D>__{a good man, kind of cheerful, reiben, here, used to call him a happy idiot.}
<C>__{reiben}
<D>__{like hell, i did.}
<C>__{ryan}
<D>__{my brothers would be mighty pissed off at me, if they knew i let some guy get killed trying to keep me alive.}
<C>__{sarge}
<D>__{you didn't let anybody get killed, you didn't even know we were coming up here.}
